TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT ONS.STUDENT_ID, ONS.ORG_NODE_ID, ONS.CUSTOMER_ID FROM ORG_NODE_STUDENT ONS
where ons.customer_id=$$CUSTOMER_ID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ORG_NODE_PARENT.PARENT_ORG_NODE_ID as PARENT_ORG_NODE_ID, ORG_NODE_PARENT.ORG_NODE_ID as ORG_NODE_ID, org_node.ORG_NODE_NAME as ORG_NODE_NAME, ORG_NODE_PARENT.CUSTOMER_ID as CUSTOMER_ID FROM ORG_NODE_PARENT,org_node WHERE org_node_parent.customer_id=org_node.customer_id and org_node_parent.org_node_id=org_node.org_node_id and org_node_parent.customer_id=$$CUSTOMER_ID ORDER BY parent_ORG_NODE_id--
